        Here are a few considerations for those interested in joining
the Guild:
 
- Take a look at the powers list and talk to members of the guild who
  have ones you're interested in.  Start thinking about what you'll want
  to get.
 
- Psionicist SP are based on Int, Wis, and Chr.  Those stats are
  slightly cheaper in guild and the physical ones (str, con, dex) are
  slightly more expensive.  Either buy up your mental stats early to
  have more SP, or buy up your physical stats at the Adventurer's Guild
  before you join (although the price difference isn't all that much).
 
- Psionicists can use short and medium weapons and most forms of
  non-torso armor.  Body armor is restricted to leather.  Start looking
  around for good armor usable by the Guild and if you're going to
  specialize in a weapon, pick something usable by the guild and start
  earning spec bonuses now.
 
